name: Warmup_Div05_Sub03
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD5S3.CPF,
GmailD5S3.NOME,
GmailD5S3.EMAIL,
GmailD5S3.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S3.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD5S3.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD5S3.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S3.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV05_SUB03 GmailD5S3
UNION
